data.description:
Welcome to the epitome of luxury living in the highly sought-after, gated community of Reds Gait! This stunning and freshly painted 5-bedroom, 4-bathroom home offers a spacious and elegant retreat with over 3,700 square feet of living space and a 3-car garage.

As you approach this exquisite residence, you'll be captivated by its charming curb appeal, featuring manicured landscaping and a welcoming front entry. Step inside, and you'll immediately be struck by the open and airy foyer that spans two stories. The heart of this home is the gourmet kitchen, complete with granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, a center island, and ample cabinet space. Whether you're a culinary enthusiast or simply enjoy hosting friends and family, this kitchen is a dream come true.

The expansive living room with a cozy fireplace and high ceilings is perfect for gatherings or relaxation. Adjacent to the living room is a formal dining room, ideal for hosting elegant dinners and celebrations.

The primary bedroom suite is a retreat in itself, featuring a spacious walk-in closet and a luxurious en-suite bathroom with dual vanities, a soaking tub, and a separate shower. Four additional well-appointed bedrooms provide ample space for family members, guests, or a home gym.

Step outside to your private backyard oasis, where you'll find a screened in lanai, lush landscaping, and plenty of room for outdoor entertaining and recreation. The three-car garage provides storage space and convenience for multiple vehicles.

Located in the exclusive Reds Gait community, you'll enjoy the benefits of security and privacy. This prime location offers easy access to shopping, dining, and major transportation routes, making it a desirable place to call home. Schedule your showing today and experience luxury living at its finest!

If buyer uses listing agents preferred lender, lender will contribute 1% of loan amount credit towards rate by down.
